<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Hi, you!</h2>
  <p>Maybe it's been another rough week and it's time that you felt better. Here's the last five things that you really liked:</p>
  <ul>
  <% @thoughts.each do |t| %>
    <li><%= t.body %></li>
  <% end %>
  </ul>
  <p>You've been great, and you're gonna carry on being great!</p>
  <p>And because you're such a mensch, here have this <%= link_to(@cute.media_type + " of " + @cute.description, @cute.url) %>!</p>
  <% if @cute.media_type == "image" %><p><img src="<%= @cute.url %>"></p><% end %>
</body>
</html>